sources.description:
To avoid a debt to a local thug (Jason Momoa), two brothers plan to fake a disappearance on an Alaskan mountaintop. But as the sheriff (Cary Elwes) becomes suspicious, the hoax turns real and a dangerous man is looking for blood.

Directed by Richard Gray
2016
Starring Jason Momoa, Cary Elwes, Melora Walters, Anna Hutchison
